articles.title: Unvaccinated Americans say the need for booster shots proves Covid vaccines don't work, Kaiser survey shows - CNBC
articles.description: A Kaiser Family Foundation survey shows that 71% percent of unvaccinated respondents said boosters are a sign that vaccines are not working.
articles.content:
